{"tid":1644232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝白警協助拆鐵","createTime":"2019-10-10T13:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:24.000Z","uid":269125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9468b0ebfecee8c71fccd090cd4f469fe1b8d7","tid":1644232,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過點解上水隻狗咁光明正大<br />\n<br />\n一當然可能係佢地蠢<br />\n不過姑且聽聽二<br />\n<br />\n上水一出咗狗，輿論即刻口殊筆伐，當中不缺以下言論：<br />\n「政府故意停鐵，阻礙市民返工」<br />\n「警方臥底嚴重破壞港鐵，做成市民不便」<br />\n<br />\n其實已經到咗十月，政府民意已經輸到貼地，佢地一早已經唔介意會唔會輸民意，佢地只係想止暴，因為和理非任你點舞都威脅唔到政府。至於國際線？人權法案過硬，點都救唔返，wfc。<br />\n俾大家見到狗臥底係黨鐵站內，大家就會一齊譴責政府，譴責狗方故意破壞黨鐵，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「妨礙市民日常生活」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n於是乎當勇武再次想主動幫黨鐵裝修時，佢地就要開始考慮：「死啦，我地再搞鐵，會唔會搞到一般人？會唔會迫走淺黃？大家都話搞鐵等同妨礙市民喎？」<br />\n<br />\n又或是各位連登仔開始怕失民意，開始各種叫停裝修黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n無論點樣，都或多或少達到止暴既效果，因為40幾個站，每個守30隻green object，千幾人無可能日日夜夜守鐵。林鄭係想借此加大大家對拆鐵既心理負擔。<br />\n<br />\n因此我地要講既唔係「譴死黑警破壞黨鐵」，而係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝白警協助拆鐵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk0YpRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk0YpRn.jpg&h=1de4f712&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e0d08181241fa497cd0ffdb8d779465aae836c9","tid":1644232,"uid":269125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"周街貼去贊揚拆鐵既白警手足唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d980965f3a9c2e7e2efd628e2d47e902908833a3","tid":1644232,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"多謝白警協助拆鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb26e08d46dcb34814f8885720c9e5e6d7269e5b","tid":1644232,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我未聽過呢個terms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4029b229d791a854779e9d2297a249b004e7cbc0","tid":1644232,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"文宣部，請宣傳下：幪面同無編號嘅黑警原因係混雜咗公安/解放軍嚟"},{"pid":"af5b25bf51d3bb5047ec39a5acf6a93725601878","tid":1644232,"uid":184903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白警??"},{"pid":"f6ba9e6d3c8939ef899c1292cfd80fcaf002e858","tid":1644232,"uid":306423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb26e08d46dcb34814f8885720c9e5e6d7269e5b","tid":1644232,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我未聽過呢個terms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"曲直不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d26a6df1ec7f454cec9453a6c0576d1fa594399","tid":1644232,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb26e08d46dcb34814f8885720c9e5e6d7269e5b","tid":1644232,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我未聽過呢個terms <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614d3be298b04c2bc77eacfae81ef357eafaecd3","tid":1644232,"uid